data.description: **Sellers are offering $8,000 for a 2/1 rate buy down to save on your interest rate with an acceptable offer.** Tremendous opportunity to own in the highly desirable Deer Hunters Run neighbor of Van Meter only 10 minutes to West Des Moines/Jordan Creek. This quiet and private neighborhood is a natures lovers dream full of timber, walking/riding trails as well as a shared private pond for fishing and non motorized equipment. This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom split level one owner home has multi level living space including a cozy sitting room with fireplace, living room, large family room, formal dining room and finished basement! The kitchen and baths all have hard surface countertops. New LVP flooring in the bedrooms and upper hallway.  The master suite has his and her closets and a wonderful master bath with large shower. The multi level deck overlooks the wooded backyard/green space which is the perfect spot to host a family gathering. The large 3 car heated garage allows for plenty of space and a workshop. Don't miss out on this gorgeous property! Call for your personal showing.
